The cave goblin '''Guards''' keep order in [[Dorgesh-Kaan]]. When spoken to they will sometimes tease the player. If the player fails to pickpocket a [[Cave goblin (Dorgesh-Kaan)|cave goblin]] in the vicinity of cave goblin guards, they may shout "Stop that!" and attack the player.

